data.description: Move-in ready Lake Cunningham home with 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car, master suite has dual sinks. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and an open concept. Nice big fenced-in back yard, fresh stain on fence and deck. The deck was enlarged for better entertaining. This home is located on a large corner lot in a quiet, friendly neighborhood. 2 large living rooms with hard surface flooring throughout the home. Ample storage space. Super easy access to interstate, lake and trails. A designer touch has been added to visual a home meant for you!
